OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FFor almost 200 years the iconic
OL,7,FBuckingham Palace has been the
OL,8,Fofficial residence of the monarch,
OL,9,Fhowever on Thursday the Palace
OL,10,Fconfirmed that is no longer the case
OL,11,Fand it will remain the King's
OL,12,F'office', ITV News Correspondent
OL,13,FGeraint Vincent reports
OL,15,FThe King and Queen will not use
OL,16,FBuckingham Palace as their personal
OL,17,Fresidence, it was revealed as royal
OL,18,Faccounts were published on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
