OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782487104
OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FThe historic building has been the
OL,7,Fofficial London residence of the
OL,8,FSovereign since 1837, when Queen
OL,9,FVictoria was on the throne.
OL,11,FIt is currently undergoing a major
OL,12,F#369 million re-servicing programme to
OL,13,Fupgrade and preserve it.
OL,15,FThe works, funded by a temporary
OL,16,Fuplift in the Sovereign Grant, started
OL,17,Fin 2017 and are set to be completed in
OL,18,F2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
