CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782487104
OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FHowever, once finished, the King and
OL,7,FQueen will not live at Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace but continue to use Clarence
OL,9,FHouse as their London home.
OL,11,FThere were assurances it will continue
OL,12,Fto be "the beating heart of the
OL,13,FMonarchy".
OL,15,FJames Chalmers, Keeper of the Privy
OL,16,FPurse, said: "This is both a change
OL,17,Ffrom the past and a recognition of the
OL,18,Ffuture.
OL,26,@tD@GOUuD@IO]xD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
