OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782487104
OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,F"Let me be clear, however, that in all
OL,7,Fother ways Buckingham Palace will
OL,8,Fcontinue to be both the ceremonial and
OL,9,Foperational centre of Royal life.
OL,11,F"It is and will remain Monarchy HQ,
OL,12,Fthe Crown Jewel of our national
OL,13,Fbuildings, with the Sovereign's
OL,14,Fstandard flying proudly from the roof
OL,15,Fwhenever His Majesty is in London,
OL,16,Fjust as it has done since Accession.
OL,18,F"The Palace will also continue as the
OL,19,Fprimary workplace of the Royal
OL,20,FHousehold."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU|D@KO]
