OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FThe King and Queen will have access to
OL,7,Fprivate rooms within Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace, where they can retire during
OL,9,Fthe day, and which could be used as
OL,10,Fresidential accommodation in the
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,FQueen Elizabeth II was the last
OL,14,Fmonarch to stay overnight at
OL,15,FBuckingham Palace in March 2020,
OL,16,Fbefore she left for Windsor Castle to
OL,17,Fisolate during the Covid 19 pandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
