OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FIn another change, the King has made
OL,7,Fhistory by becoming the first monarch
OL,8,Fto release his total personal tax
OL,9,Fpayment in a bid to ensure more
OL,10,Ftransparency around royal finances.
OL,12,FCharles voluntarily pays income tax on
OL,13,Fhis private income and capital gains
OL,14,Ftax on relevant elements of his assets.
OL,16,FMr Chalmers said: "When Prince of
OL,17,FWales, His Majesty disclosed his tax,
OL,18,Fand he has asked that we make public
OL,19,Fhis combined income and capital gains
OL,20,Ftax payments as king.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
