OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782487105
OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,F"Today I can share with you that His
OL,7,FMajesty's tax payable for 2024-25 was
OL,8,F#12.9 million.
OL,10,F"If annual media league tables are to
OL,11,Fbe believed on such matters, that
OL,12,Fplaces His Majesty among the top 100
OL,13,Ftaxpayers in the country for that
OL,14,Fyear."
