OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FPrivate income is a combination of the
OL,7,Fincome from the Duchy of Lancaster,
OL,8,Fhis own personal investment portfolio
OL,9,Fand his estates.
OL,11,FPrince William has followed suit and
OL,12,Falso revealed his tax bill for the
OL,13,Ffirst time.
OL,15,FWilliam receives an income from the
OL,16,FDuchy of Cornwall, a hereditary estate
OL,17,Ffeaturing The Oval cricket ground and
OL,18,Fproviding the heir to the throne with
OL,19,Ffunds, independent of the Monarch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
