OL,3,CKing and Queen will not live at
OL,4,CBuckingham Palace
OL,6,FHe pays tax voluntarily on income that
OL,7,Fis not used to meet official
OL,8,Fexpenditure.
OL,10,FDuring the 2024-25 financial year his
OL,11,Ftax bill was #7.76 million in income
OL,12,Fand capital gains tax and was #8.34
OL,13,Fmillion in 2023-24.
OL,15,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,16,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,17,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,18,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
